http://www.lol.shareworld.com:80/zmi/roningen.htm 199.172.47.21 19970111021255 text/html 10389
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Microsoft-IIS/2.0
Date: Sat, 11 Jan 1997 02:08:18 GMT
