<html>

<head>
<title>Z Magazine: What's New</title>
<meta name="GENERATOR" content="Microsoft FrontPage 1.1">
</head>

<body bgcolor="#EEFFFA" link="#CC0000" vlink="#000055" alink="#FF3300">
<h2><img src="../gifs/blnew.gif" alt="What's New at Z Magazine" align=top hspace=4 width=45 height=54> <img src="../gifs/lgnew.gif" align=top hspace=4 width=254 height=27> <img src="../gifs/oldsmzma.gif" align=bottom width=108 height=37></h2>
<blockquote>
<p>Here are some updates to the Z Magazine pages as of 18 June 1996. </p>
<ul>
<li>We have entered a host of new articles. </li>
</ul>
<p>Feel free to let us know what you think of the changes, and drop us any ideas about additions or alterations you may have. </p>
</blockquote>
</body>

