<html>

<head>
<title>ZMI Agenda Frame</title>
<meta name="GENERATOR" content="Microsoft FrontPage 1.1">
<meta name="FORMATTER" content="Microsoft FrontPage 2.0">
</head>

<body stylesrc="../zmag/about.htm">

<p><a href="index.htm"><img src="../gifs/titzmi.gif"
alt="Z Magazine" align="top" border="0" width="121" height="95"></a> </p>

<h2>Purposes and Policies</h2>

<p>Z Media Institute exists to share knowledge, skills, and
information relevant to working effectively with media in the
United States. The program emphasizes the shortcomings of
mainstream media and the possibilities of alternative media. It
is an intense 9 day gathering with courses four times each day,
and events and speakers every night. There is radio and computer
equipment on hand, for technical training, etc.</p>

<p>ZMI incorporates courses in political theory, media studies,
organizational skills, and technical skills, with project groups
in radio, print, and organizing work.</p>

<p>The goal of ZMI is to help progressive people initiate or work
more effectively within alternative media or activist
institutions, and to better media and its uses.</p>

<hr>

<h2>Financing and Budget</h2>

<p>ZMI's costs (estimated here for the June 1995 session) are
room and board for all attendees and faculty ($47,000), staff and
lecturer's fees and travel expenses ($7,500), computer rentals,
text production, and general miscellaneous costs ($3,500), for a
total of $58,000.</p>

<p>ZMI's revenues are the fees paid by students. The full price
is $1,000. Scholarships range from $250 to $750. We are still
arranging fees and acceptances for June 1995, but the goal is to
schedule income of about $60,000 for the 80 attending students. </p>

<p>There is, regrettably, no outside funding support for ZMI. On
the other hand much of the staff and faculty time is donated.</p>

<p>Anyone who wishes to help ZMI by providing funds that will
enable an expansion of scholarships, can do so by making a tax
deductible donation. Call 508-548-9063 for more information.</p>

<hr>
</body>
</html>
