<dl>
    <dt>The first thing to find out about any school, university,
        etc., is who is doing the teaching. In the case of ZMI,
        in fact, the &quot;student body&quot; is often also so
        talented and diverse that it is itself a fantastic
        resource. But, our faculty and staff is pretty good
        too...</dt>
