</h3>

<H3>Urgent!</h3>

Mark Achbar, producer of the award-winning documentary
<em>Manufacturing Consent: Noam Chomsky and the Media</em>, <a href
="http://www.well.com/www/srhodes/chomsky.html">needs your help <strong>right
now</strong></a> to lobby local PBS affiliates to air the film.

<H3>The Latest</H3>
From <a href="http://www.lbbs.org/ZMag.htm"><em>Z Magazine</em></a>:
<UL>
<LI>``<a href="ftp://ftp.cs.cmu.edu/user/cap/chomsky/updates/articles/chomsky.-z.rollback-part1">Rollback, part I</a>'' (January 1995) [01 March 1995]
<LI>``<a href="ftp://ftp.cs.cmu.edu/user/cap/chomsky/updates/articles/chomsky.-z.rollback-part2">Rollback, part II</a>'' (February 1995) [23 February 1995]
