</UL>

<P>Look in the ``<a
href="chomsky/archive/updates/">updates</a>''
directory for a spate of updates from last year.

<HR> <em><strong>Please note:</strong> The ftp site on which the
Archive resides is typically subject to a <strong>huge</strong> volume
of traffic.  If you get an error message, just try again in a few
minutes, or especially at non-peak hours (GMT -0500).</em>

<P>I will make announcements (among other channels) to <a
href="news:alt.fan.noam-chomsky"><em>alt.fan.noam-chomsky</em></a> and
<a
href="ftp://pencil.cs.missouri.edu/WEB/map.html"><em>misc.activism.progressive</EM></a>.
Meanwhile, please send along any ideas . . . as well as your
suggestions or comments.  I very much appreciate all feedback.
