<body background="images/blutxtr3.jpg" bgcolor="#A4B1B9">
<h1><font color="#0000A0"><font size=7><em><strong>ShareWorld Kids</strong></em></font></font></h1>
<p><a href="swindex.htm"><img src="images/bhome.gif" alt="[Home Icon]" align=bottom border=0 width=56 height=14></a><a href="news.htm"><img src="images/bnews.gif" alt="[What's New Icon]" align=bottom border=0 width=58 height=14></a><a href="serv01.htm"><img src="images/bservs.gif" alt="[Products Icon]" align=bottom border=0 width=57 height=14></a><a href="feedback.htm"><img src="images/bfeed.gif" alt="[Feedback Icon]" align=bottom border=0 width=59 height=14></a></p>
<p><img src="images/div.gif" alt="[HRule Image]" align=bottom width=465 height=7> </p>
<h2>ShareWorld Children's Offerings</h2>
<p>On ShareWorld we take young people seriously. They can participate in forums, of course. But they also have their own forums, 
no adults allowed. And their own pen pal system, games to play, browsing help, and school help. And for older &quot;children&quot; we are 
hard to work on an online high school system offering typical high school type courses, but with a socially conscious attitude and 
content. </p>
<p>Our systems also incorporate browser controls.</p>
<p><img src="images/SWkids13.gif" align=bottom width=580 height=479></p>
<p>To find out more about our systems, their options and functionality, and how our clients and users benefit, please choose <a href="serv01.htm">services</a>, 
here or above. </p>
<p><img src="images/div.gif" alt="[HRule Image]" align=bottom width=465 height=7> </p>
