<DOCHDR>
http://www.lol.shareworld.com:80/aboutlolu.htm 199.172.47.21 19970111023650 text/html 2897
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Microsoft-IIS/2.0
Date: Sat, 11 Jan 1997 02:32:29 GMT
