<h2>What Is Left On Line?</h2>
<p><font size=3><img src="images/grnhat.gif" align=bottom width=32 height=32> Left On Line (or LOL) is a sophisticated private web site with diverse extra-web 
functionality but simple design and graphics for easy, efficient, navigation. It is a continuous 
town meeting, an intellectual and activist service center for large sectors of the progressive 
community. It is a place to...</font></p>
<blockquote>
<dl>
