<dt><font size=3><img src="images/grnarrow.gif" align=baseline width=24 height=13> enjoy and educate oneself </font></dt>
<dt><font size=3><img src="images/grnarrow.gif" align=baseline width=24 height=13> browse the WWW with guidance</font></dt>
</dl>
</blockquote>
