<h2>ShareWorld Socializing</h2>
<p>On ShareWorld there are a variety of ways to socialize with other adults, teleconferencing, playing games, sharing information. 
But first you have to meet one another, and for that we have a special little module...</p>
<p><img src="images/SWadul14.gif" align=bottom width=527 height=503></p>
<p>You just choose an option, find a likely person (or add yourself to a list) and strike up an acquaintance.</p>
<p>To find out more about our systems, their options and functionality, and how our clients and users benefit, please choose <a href="serv01.htm">services</a>, 
here or above. </p>
