<DOCOLDNO>IA027-000290-B008-188</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://www.lol.shareworld.com:80/issue1up.htm 199.172.47.21 19970111030001 text/html 9133
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Microsoft-IIS/2.0
Date: Sat, 11 Jan 1997 02:55:16 GMT
