<dd><b><i><font SIZE=-1><a href="http://www.dnai.com/~children/">Children
Now is a non-partisan non-profit organization dedicated to protecting the
rights and welfare of children. </a></font></i></b></dd>

<dt>
<hr></dt>

<dt><b><i><a href="http://www.cpsr.org/home.html">Computer Professionals
