<dd><b><i><font SIZE=-1><a href="http://www.cpsr.org/home.html">CPSR, which
recently revamped its web site, is a non-profit organization concerned
with the effects of computers on society. Of particular interest on the
CPSR home page is a page of articles about </a><a href="http://www.cpsr.org/dox/gender.html">gender
issues</a><a href="http://www.cpsr.org/home.html"> and computing. </a></font></i></b></dd>

