<dd><b><i><font SIZE=-1><a href="http://www.eic.org">A self-described &quot;war
room&quot; to combat the Republican majority in Congress as it attempts
to gut environmental policy. The site is packed with news, information
and opportunities for action. </a></font></i></b></dd>

<dt>
