<dt><b><i><a href="http://www.gdn.org/">Global Democracy Network </a></i></b></dt>

<dd><b><i><font SIZE=-1><a href="http://www.gdn.org/">A searchable stockpile
of documents related to international human rights. Though human rights
issues is the focus of this site, it also includes links to governmental
information of nearly 30 nations. </a></font></i></b></dd>

<dt><b><i><a href="http://www.greenpeace.org/">Greenpeace International
</a></i></b></dt>

<dd><b><i><font SIZE=-1><a href="http://www.greenpeace.org/">This is the
