<hr></dt>

<dt><b><i><a href="http://www.house.gov/democrats/welcome.html">House Democrats
Home Page </a></i></b></dt>

<dd><b><i><font SIZE=-1><a href="http://www.house.gov/democrats/welcome.html">Rep.
Richard Gephardt, Democratic minority leader, has established the House
Democrats Home Page which offers updates on current legislation, profiles
of Democratic leaders, and press releases. </a></font></i></b></dd>

