<DOCHDR>
http://www.lol.shareworld.com:80/parecon/intro.htm 199.172.47.21 19970111032544 text/html 15077
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Microsoft-IIS/2.0
Date: Sat, 11 Jan 1997 03:21:20 GMT
Content-Type: text/html
Accept-Ranges: bytes
Last-Modified: Thu, 24 Oct 1996 15:37:01 GMT
