<h1><font color="#0000A0"><font size=7><em><strong>ShareWorld Schools</strong></em></font></font></h1>
<p><a href="swindex.htm"><img src="images/bhome.gif" alt="[Home Icon]" align=bottom border=0 width=56 height=14></a><a href="news.htm"><img src="images/bnews.gif" alt="[What's New Icon]" align=bottom border=0 width=58 height=14></a><a href="serv01.htm"><img src="images/bservs.gif" alt="[Products Icon]" align=bottom border=0 width=57 height=14></a><a href="feedback.htm"><img src="images/bfeed.gif" alt="[Feedback Icon]" align=bottom border=0 width=59 height=14></a></p>
<p><img src="images/div.gif" alt="[HRule Image]" align=bottom width=465 height=7> </p>
<h2>ShareWorld University and High Schools On Line</h2>
<p>One of the most interesting uses of telecommunications is for education. Though university level courses generally cost upwards 
of $1500, on ShareWorld full ten week courses, with lectures, readings, faculty participation in weekly discussions, etc., average 
only $50 a semester. There are diverse faculty from the sponsoring organizations, from universities, with practical experience, 
etc. Really, a remarkable selection of people. </p>
<p>Here is the window from which one gets information about the online schools. Taking courses is done in closed forums.</p>
<p><img src="images/SWscho9.gif" align=bottom width=530 height=417></p>
<p>To find out more about our systems, their options and functionality, and how our clients and users benefit, please choose <a href="serv01.htm">services</a>, 
here or above. </p>
<p><img src="images/div.gif" alt="[HRule Image]" align=bottom width=465 height=7> </p>
<h2>Contact Information</h2>
<dl>
<dt><strong>Telephone</strong> </dt>
<dd>1-617-862-4500</dd>
<dt><strong>FAX</strong> </dt>
<dd>fax number here</dd>
<dt><strong>Postal address</strong> </dt>
<dd>address here...</dd>
<dt><strong>Electronic mail</strong> </dt>
<dd>General Information: <a href="mailto:gcigale@sharegroup.com">gcigale@sharegroup.com</a><br>
Webmaster: <a href="mailto:sysop@lbbs.org">sysop@lbbs.org</a></dd>
</dl>
