<dt>
<hr></dt>

<dt><b><i><a href="http://www.newparty.org/">The New Party </a></i></b></dt>

<dd><b><i><font SIZE=-1><a href="http://www.newparty.org/">The New Party
is just what the name implies. It is a progressive alternative to the two-party
system, promoting an agenda that includes campaign finance reform, improving
public schools, universal voter registration, creating family supporting
jobs without wrecking the environment, raising the minimum wage and universal
access to health care. For now it is focusing on local offices, but it
has high hopes. </a></font></i></b></dd>

<dt>
<hr></dt>

<dt><b><i><a href="http://www.outnow.com">OutNOW! Alive </a></i></b></dt>

