<h1><font color="#0000A0"><font size=7><em><strong>ShareWorld Activism</strong></em></font></font></h1>
<p><a href="swindex.htm"><img src="images/bhome.gif" alt="[Home Icon]" align=bottom border=0 width=56 height=14></a><a href="news.htm"><img src="images/bnews.gif" alt="[What's New Icon]" align=bottom border=0 width=58 height=14></a><a href="serv01.htm"><img src="images/bservs.gif" alt="[Products Icon]" align=bottom border=0 width=57 height=14></a><a href="feedback.htm"><img src="images/bfeed.gif" alt="[Feedback Icon]" align=bottom border=0 width=59 height=14></a></p>
<p><img src="images/div.gif" alt="[HRule Image]" align=bottom width=465 height=7> </p>
<h2>ShareWorld Activism</h2>
<p>There are two primary facilities for promoting online activism on ShareWorld Systems. First, there are 
offerings which allow folks to share information, develop agendas, etc. These include the forums, mailing 
lists, the calendar, etc., tools for altering and updating these, for joining active groups, etc.</p>
<p>There is also, however, a tool specifically geared to using email and fax capabilities to make positions 
widely known and pressure officials. First you choose an area of concern, as in this listing from 
Wilderness On Line...</p>
<p><img src="images/SWacti16.gif" align=bottom width=508 height=352></p>
<p>Then you indicate your locale and choose a recipient...</p>
<p><img src="images/SWacti17.gif" align=bottom width=770 height=437></p>
<p>And next you adapt a sample message and either E-Mail it or fax it...</p>
<p><img src="images/SWacti18.gif" align=bottom width=783 height=552></p>
<p>To find out more about our systems, their options and functionality, and how our clients and users benefit, 
please choose <a href="serv01.htm">services</a>, here or above. </p>
<p><img src="images/div.gif" alt="[HRule Image]" align=bottom width=465 height=7> </p>
