<h2>Terms</h2>

<blockquote>
    <p>Joining LOL involves no initial fee. When you join you get
    3 free hours or fifteen days, whichever comes first, to
    explore the system and its offerings. At that point, and only
    at that point, we begin charging you the monthly fee. You can
    quit, from online, any time.</p>
    <p>And there is only one monthly fee, simple but inflexible. </p>
    <p>For your membership you pay $8 a month and get unlimited
    access via your web browser (and our plug in modules) to LOL
    options including online articles, search facilities, forums,
    polling, calendars, web guidance, games, email, and so on. </p>
    <p>It doesn't matter how much you use the system, how much
    email you do, how many forum messages you read or write, how
    much you listen to or contribute, or view, within the LOL
    system and the broader ShareWorld community of systems. It is
    $8 a month, period.</p>
    <dl>
        <dt>&nbsp;</dt>
    </dl>
</blockquote>

<h2>Join From Online</h2>

<blockquote>
    <p>To join from online just navigate to the <a
    href="http://www.lol.shareworld.com/leftonl/lolentry.htm"
    target="_top">Left On Line Vistors</a> page, and from there
    peruse the availabilities, and then, if you decide you want
    to join, select the join option and enter your information.</p>
</blockquote>

