<hr>
<blockquote>
<p>The Left On Line University (another name for the 
ShareWorld Systems Ideas on Line University) provides 
three semesters per year of non-jargonistic, university level, 
fifteen-week courses accessible via the Left On Line 
communications system in political, social, economic, 
historical, and activist topics. Notable faculty have included 
Noam Chomsky, Howard Zinn, Juliet Schor, Michael Albert, 
Holly Sklar, Robin Hahnel, Steven Shalom, and others.</p>
<p>Courses will begin anew in the first week of October, 1996. 
To take courses you must join <a href="http://www.lol.shareworld.com/leftonl/lolhome.htm" target="_top">The Left On Line System</a>.</p>
