<h1><a name="order">To Order Books from South End Press</a></h1>
<ul>
<li>Order by E-Mail at 10% Off All Listed Prices</li>
</ul>
<p>All orders must be pre-paid. Send us the title, number of copies, your mailing address, and credit card 
info to South End Press Order Department at <a href="mailto:south.end.press@lbbs.org">south.end.press@lbbs.org</a> Be sure to list your name as it 
appears on the card and your card number and expiration date. We'll charge you $3.00 for the first book 
and 75 cents for each additional book.</p>
<ul>
<li>Become a member</li>
</ul>
<p>Get 2 free books and a 40% discount on all orders for a year. Only $40 to $149 will do it. $150 makes 
you a Sustainer, earning you 5 free paperbacks and a 40% discount on all orders for a year; $1,000 makes 
you a Lifetime Sustainer, earning you any backlist title you want plus a 40% discount on all future orders, 
period. Write to South End Press, 116 Saint Botolph Street, boston, MA 02115. Or e-mail 
<a href="mailto:south.end.press@lbbs.org">south.end.press@lbbs.org</a>.</p>
<ul>
<li>Order by Phone</li>
</ul>
<p>Call 800-533-8478 to place an order by phone at 10% off. Have your credit card ready...</p>
<ul>
<li>Order by Snail Mail</li>
</ul>
<p>Send your check, money order, or credit card to Order Department, South End Press, 116 Saint Botolph 
Street, Boston, MA 02115. </p>
